<h1>便</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">biàn</span><span class=alesi>(bian4)</span> , <span style="color:#cc7700;">pián</span><span class=alesi>(pian2)</span> , <span style="color:#990000;">biān</span><span class=alesi>(bian1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 便 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 便</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/convenience" style="color:black;">convenience</a>, <a href="/dictionary/ease" style="color:black;">ease</a>; <a href="/dictionary/expedient" style="color:black;">expedient</a></p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 9<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 9 strokes: <a href="/character/是" title="shi4: indeed, yes, right; to be; demonstrative pronoun, this, that">是</a>, <a href="/character/说" title="shuo1: speak, say, talk; scold, upbraid">说</a>, <a href="/character/要" title="yao4: necessary, essential; necessity">要</a>, <a href="/character/种" title="zhong3: seed; race, breed; to plant">种</a>, <a href="/character/面" title="mian4: face; surface; plane; side, dimension">面</a>, <a href="/character/看" title="kan4: look, see; examine, scrutinize">看</a>, <a href="/character/前" title="qian2: in front, forward; preceding">前</a>, <a href="/character/点" title="dian3: dot, speck, spot; point, degree">点</a>, <a href="/character/将" title="jiang1: will, going to, future; general">将</a>, <a href="/character/很" title="hen3: very, quite, much">很</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/人" title="Kangxi radical 9">人</a>&nbsp;9.7</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 2 <br><small>Other HSK 2 characters: <a href="/character/司" title="si1: take charge of, control, manage; officer">司</a>, <a href="/character/眼" title="yan3: eye; eyelet, hole, opening">眼</a>, <a href="/character/非" title="fei1: not, negative, non-; oppose">非</a>, <a href="/character/白" title="bai2: white; pure, unblemished; bright">白</a>, <a href="/character/件" title="jian4: numerary adjunct for article; matter">件</a>, <a href="/character/场" title="chang3: open space, field, market">场</a>, <a href="/character/务" title="wu4: affairs, business; must, should">务</a>, <a href="/character/思" title="si1: think, consider, ponder; final particle">思</a>, <a href="/character/完" title="wan2: complete, finish, settle; whole">完</a>, <a href="/character/色" title="se4: color, tint, hue, shade; form, body; beauty, desire for beauty">色</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-2" title="List of HSK 2 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 2 charaters &raquo;</a></small></p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 271</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 1556</p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/不便" title="bu4 bian4">不便</a>, <a href="/dictionary/乘便" title="cheng2 bian4">乘便</a>, <a href="/dictionary/二便" title="er4 bian4">二便</a>, <a href="/dictionary/以便" title="yi3 bian4">以便</a>, <a href="/dictionary/任便" title="ren4 bian4">任便</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便中" title="bian4 zhong1">便中</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便人" title="bian4 ren2">便人</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便便" title="bian4 bian4">便便</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便便" title="pian2 pian2">便便</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便函" title="bian4 han2">便函</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便利" title="bian4 li4">便利</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便器" title="bian4 qi4">便器</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便士" title="bian4 shi4">便士</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便壶" title="bian4 hu2">便壶</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便嬛" title="pian2 xuan1">便嬛</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便宜" title="bian4 yi2">便宜</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便宜" title="pian2 yi5">便宜</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便宴" title="bian4 yan4">便宴</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便帽" title="bian4 mao4">便帽</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便急" title="bian4 ji2">便急</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便所" title="bian4 suo3">便所</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便捷" title="bian4 jie2">便捷</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便于" title="bian4 yu2">便于</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便是" title="bian4 shi4">便是</a>, <a href="/dictionary/便服" title="bian4 fu2">便服</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">便[<span style="color:#000099;">biàn</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- ordinary<br>- plain<br>- convenient<br>- as convenient<br>- when the chance arises<br>- handy<br>- easy<br>- informal<br>- simple<br>- so<br>- thus<br>- to relieve oneself<br>- to urinate<br>- to defecate<br>- equivalent to <a href="/dictionary/就">就</a>[jiu4]: then<br>- in that case<br>- even if<br>- soon afterwards<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">便[<span style="color:#cc7700;">pián</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- advantageous<br>- cheap<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+4FBF</p></div>

